Package aas_core.aas3_0.types.model

Interface IOperation

All Superinterfaces:
IClass, IHasDataSpecification, IHasExtensions, IHasSemantics, IQualifiable, IReferable, ISubmodelElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
EnhancedOperation, Operation
public interface IOperation extends ISubmodelElement
An operation is a submodel element with input and output variables.

Constraints:

  • Constraint AASd-134: For an Operation the IReferable.getIdShort() of all OperationVariable.getValue()'s in getInputVariables(), getOutputVariables() and getInoutputVariables() shall be unique.
